text: Bilyk () is a Ukrainian surname derived from a word meaning "white" (білий). It may refer to: *Catryna Bilyk (born 1959), Australian politician *Jeff Bilyk (born 1977), American association football player *Iryna Bilyk (born 1970), Ukrainian singer *Iryney Bilyk (born 1950), Ukrainian Greek-Catholic hierarch *Luke Bilyk (born 1994), Canadian actor *Nikola Bilyk (born 1996), Austrian handball player *Oleh Bilyk (born 1998), Ukrainian football player ==See also== *Bilyi Category:Ukrainian-language surnames
title: Bilyk
